{"first_name": "Eric", "last_name": "Cunningham", "work_email_status": "good", "work_email_quality": "ok", "work_email_confidence": "99%", "primary_work_email_source": "A-Leads", "country": "United States", "seniority": "Owner", "departments": "C-Suite", "personal_linkedin": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/ericocunningham", "company_linkedin": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/gc-plumbing-services", "company_summary": "GC Plumbing Services is an established and reliable family-owned company providing residential plumbing services. We operate with integrity, accountability, and a growth mindset, and we demonstrate service, excellence, and trust to our valued customers. Every service issue adds stress to a homeowner’s life, and we strive to resolve their issue in a manner that eliminates that stress and delivers an exceptional experience. Our vision is to raise the bar in the residential plumbing services industry. We aim to create the best place in Austin for professional plumbers to work, and to embody excellence and service in the local community.

If you need a plumber, our team of professional technicians offers high-quality services for both residential and commercial buildings. Since 1998, we’ve been serving Central Texas with our professional services and personal care. Owner, Eric Cunningham, and Responsible Master Plumber, Glenn Coburn Jr., believe there is more to plumbing than simply fixing broken pipes. They are committed to providing clients with the best customer care in the industry.
As an accredited member of the Better Business Bureau, GC Plumbing Services provides a wide range of services to improve the condition of your plumbing system. In addition to regular plumbing services – such as pipe repair and plumbing fixture services – we also provide gas line repair, water heater repair, and a variety of water treatment services.", "num_employees": "2-10 employees", "company_country": "United States", "technologies": ["amp", "quickbooks"], "facebook": "https://www.facebook.com/gcplumbingtx", "twitter": "https://www.twitter.com/plumbing_gc", "instagram": "https://www.instagram.com/goodcleanplumbing"}

