We are experts in the field of exterior finishes, and specialize in high end residential and commercial grade products. Our specialties include, but are not limited to, Exterior Insulation Finishing Systems (EIFS), 3-Coat Cement Stucco/Plaster, Thin Brick & Cultured Stone veneers, Secondary Air/Moisture Barriers, and many other specialty finishes.

Nearly all of our business comes from referrals by previously satisfied clients thanks to our commitment to maintaining positive relationships before, during, and after working on a project. We understand the importance of working together as a team to complete a project in a timely manner without sacrificing the quality that our clients have come to expect. We take pride in giving your building the 'finishing touch' that will last a lifetime.", "num_employees": "2-10 employees", "company_country": "United States", "technologies": ["amp"], "facebook": "https://www.facebook.com/superior-designs-inc-427453687374820"}

