{"first_name": "Roger", "last_name": "Laduke", "work_email_status": "good", "work_email_quality": "ok", "work_email_confidence": "99%", "primary_work_email_source": "A-Leads", "country": "United States", "seniority": "President/Vice President", "departments": "C-Suite", "personal_linkedin": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/roger-laduke-65127128", "company_linkedin": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/laduke-corporation", "company_summary": "LaDuke Roofing & Sheet Metal will celebrate it’s 82nd year in business in 2014, as a third generation company specializing in commercial and industrial roofing and custom architectural sheet metal. We are experienced with the installation of built-up roofing, including both asphalt and coal tar pitch, modified roofing, and single ply roofing, such as PVC, TPO, or EPDM. Our sheet metal department is among the best in the industry; skilled in both fabrication and installation of custom architectural sheet metal, including metal copings, roofing, and siding as well as many other roof related metal components. 

 LaDuke Roofing & Sheet Metal is also proud to be among the first roofing companies nationally to be ISO 9002 certified. This process has helped us to streamline our operations and procedures and really provide a better quality and faster service to our customers. We are also proficient in AutoCad Lite, a program used for designing and developing drawings and details necessary in the construction of some projects. We are members of both the National and Southeastern Roofing Contractors Associations and the Sheet Metal & Air Conditioning Contractors Association as well. 
.", "num_employees": "2-10 employees", "company_country": "United States", "technologies": ["well"], "facebook": "https://www.facebook.com/pages/laduke-roofing-sheet-metal/290917950167", "annual_revenue": "53104449"}

