{"first_name": "Jessica", "last_name": "Ellinger", "work_email_status": "good", "work_email_quality": "ok", "work_email_confidence": "99%", "primary_work_email_source": "A-Leads", "country": "United States", "seniority": "Specialist", "departments": "Marketing", "personal_linkedin": "https://www.linkedin.com/in/jessicaellinger", "company_linkedin": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/villa-lagoon-tile", "company_summary": "Villa Lagoon Tile is the premier distributor of encaustic cement tile both domestically and globally. Cement Tile is known globally by many names, Cuban tile, Moroccan tile, Mission Tile, and Mosaicos Hidraulicos to name a few.

Every cement tile is a hand-crafted work of art, with patterns formed by arranging mineral-pigmented cement blends in a mold, before being subjected to a hydraulic press and set to cure. Villa Lagoon Tile sources only the finest of these tiles through manufacturing partnerships in Vietnam, Mexico, the Caribbean, and Morocco.

Villa Lagoon Tile serves in-stock cement tile through its warehouse at the home office in Gulf Shores, AL, and ships custom tile throughout the world, including Europe, Asia, and Australia. Villa Lagoon Tile also provides custom tile creation with limitless possibilities, and hundreds of standard and exclusive patterns.", "num_employees": "2-10 employees", "company_country": "United States", "facebook": "https://www.facebook.com/villalagoontile/?ref=page_internal", "twitter": "https://www.twitter.com/villalagoontile", "youtube": "https://www.youtube.com/user/villalagoontile", "instagram": "https://www.instagram.com/villalagoontile", "annual_revenue": "368152"}

